Template Installation

# To remove all node dependencies
 $ sudo apt-get remove --purge nodejs ^node-* nodejs-*

# Install Update node package via curl
 $ curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_11.x | sudo -E bash -

 $ sudo apt-get install -y nodejs
 $ node -v && npm -v
End of Local environment setup.

Now vue paper them installation

1. Extract the to a local directory.
2. Jump in to them forlder via terminal then

	$ npm install
	$ npm run dev

	$ npm i -f ## if you found any problem try this.
	$ npm audit fix --force
	$ npm rebuild node-sass

End of the story 'I think that will make you shiny.' Goodluck!
